{"tid":2122505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學凌晨疑遭投擲汽油彈】","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:08:37.000Z","uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3a8a118d9c98a132c306f2dfcaefd3e78c052b","tid":2122505,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:44:17.000Z","msg":"【青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學凌晨疑遭投擲汽油彈】<br />\n<br />\n青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學正門，凌晨懷疑遭投擲易燃物及起火，消防員到場將火救熄，事件中無人受傷，警方將案件列作縱火案處理，由葵青警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，凌晨近1時，接獲學校保安報案後指，兩名身穿黑色上衣及黑色褲的男子形跡可疑，之後發現學校正門起火，兩名男子隨後向青康路方向逃去。警員到場發現學校正門牆壁及花槽有被燒過的痕跡，初步調查相信起火原因有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n有市民在社交網頁表示，起火前聽到兩聲巨響，網上片段中可見，學校正門入口頂部起火，消防員到場將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n九龍樂善堂發表聲明，對於梁植偉紀念中學凌晨被投擲汽油彈一事深感憤慨，事件現交由警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #青衣樂善堂梁植偉紀念中學 #縱火案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑社會定黑警做"},{"pid":"c3f77b3ab9e22ddc874a026ea365c59cc906ce8a","tid":2122505,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539623-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539623-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6MZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=86ea1619\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539623-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed19a580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539623-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"085b5cb1fe1e184cac94f1ac5a6b20b20554ad4d","tid":2122505,"uid":145273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi